      "text": [
        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"اَلتَّاجِرُ فَاجِرٌ وَ اَلْفَاجِرُ فِي اَلنَّارِ إِلاَّ مَنْ أَخَذَ اَلْحَقَّ وَ أَعْطَى اَلْحَقَّ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3729 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"The trader is sinful, and the sinful one is in the Fire-except for the one who takes what is right and gives what is right.\""
        ]
      }
    },
